methods.close:
Closes the stream and releases any system resources associated with
 it.
methods.read:
Reads characters into an array

:param buffer: (char[]) - Destination buffer
:param offset: (int) - Offset at which to start storing characters
:param len: (int) - The maximum possible number of characters to read
:return: (int) The number of characters read, or -1 if all read
